        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml School Management System\n\nleft to right direction\nskinparam linetype polyline\n\nactor \&quot;Teacher\&quot; as T\nactor \&quot;Teacher\&quot; as TR\nactor \&quot;Class Teacher\&quot; as CT\nactor \&quot;Class Teacher\&quot; as CTR\nactor \&quot;Sectional Head\&quot; as SH\nactor \&quot;Sectional Head\&quot; as SHR\nactor \&quot;Student\&quot; as S\nactor \&quot;Student\&quot; as SR\nactor \&quot;Principal\&quot; as P\nactor \&quot;Principal\&quot; as PR\nactor \&quot;Vice Principal\&quot; as VP\nactor \&quot;Vice Principal\&quot; as VPR\nactor \&quot;Administrator\&quot; as A\nactor \&quot;User\&quot; as U\nactor \&quot;User\&quot; as UR\n\nU &lt;|-- T\nU &lt;|-- S\nU &lt;|-- VP\nU &lt;|-- A\nT &lt;|-- CT\nT &lt;|-- SH\nVP &lt;|-- P\n\nrectangle \&quot;School Management System\&quot; {\n        SH -- (Access Exam Dashboard)\n        (Access Exam Dashboard) &lt;.. (Create Exams) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Exam Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Exams) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Exam Dashboard) &lt;.. (Delete Exams) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Create Exams) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Teachers): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Exams) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Teachers): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Delete Exams) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Teachers): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        SH -- (Access Staff Management Dashboard as a Teacher)\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Schedule Sectional Staff Meetings) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Create Time Tables) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Update Time Tables) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Delete Time Tables) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        \n        (Schedule Sectional Staff Meetings) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Teachers) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Create Time Tables) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Teachers): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Time Tables) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Teachers) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        \n        (Send Notifications to Sectional Head) -- SHR\n\n        T -- (Access Educational Content Dashboard)\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (View Student Activity) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Grade Student Activity) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Send Feedback and Assessments) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Create Educational Content) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Educational Content) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Delete Educational Content) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (View Time Table) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Grade Student Activity) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Send Feedback and Assessments) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Create Educational Content) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Educational Content) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Delete Educational Content) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        T -- (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard)\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Add Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Remove Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Create Competitions) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Create Societies and Clubs) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Monitor Societies and Clubs) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Delete Societies and Clubs) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Societies and Clubs) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Add Members) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Remove Members) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Members) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Create Competitions) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Create Societies and Clubs) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Societies and Clubs) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        T -- (Access Students Management Dashboard as a Teacher)\n        (Access Students Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Update Student Information) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Students Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Delete Student Information) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Students Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Create Student Information) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Students Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (View Student Performance) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Students Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Update Student Performance) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Students Management Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (View Student Attendance) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        T -- (Access Exam Dashboard as a Teacher)\n        (Access Exam Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (View Exam Results) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Exam Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Enter Exam Results) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Exam Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Update Exam Results) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Exam Dashboard as a Teacher) &lt;.. (Delete Exams Results) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Enter Exam Results) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Exam Results) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        \n        T -- (Access Query Dashboard)\n        (Access Query Dashboard) &lt;.. (Submit Leaves and Short Leaves) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Query Dashboard) &lt;.. (View Student Queries) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Query Dashboard) &lt;.. (Feedback Student Queries) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Submit Leaves and Short Leaves) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Feedback Student Queries) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Send Notifications to Teachers) -- TR\n\n        CT -- (Generate Student Reports)\n        (Generate Student Reports) &lt;.. (Student Attendance Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Generate Student Reports) &lt;.. (Student Performance Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        \n        (Student Performance Reports) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Students) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Student Performance Reports) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Sectional Head) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Student Attendance Reports) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Sectional Head) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Send Notifications to Class Teachers) -- CTR\n        (Generate Student Payment Receipts) -- CTR\n\n        S -- (Access Educational Content Dashboard as a Student)\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (View Educational Content) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (View Assessments) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (Submit Assessments) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (Update Assessments) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Educational Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (View Time Tables) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Submit Assessments) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Class Teachers): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Assessments) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Class Teachers): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        S -- (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard as a Student)\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (Apply for Societies and Clubs) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Extracurricular Content Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (Apply for Competitions) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Apply for Societies and Clubs) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Class Teachers): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Apply for Competitions) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Class Teachers): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        S -- (Access Exam Dashboard as a Student)\n        (Access Exam Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (View Exams as a Student) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Exam Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (View Exam Results as a Student) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        S -- (Access Payment Dashboard)\n        (Access Payment Dashboard) &lt;.. (Pay School Fees) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Payment Dashboard) &lt;.. (Pay Welfare Fees) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Pay School Fees) ..&gt; (Generate Student Payment Receipts) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Pay Welfare Fees) ..&gt; (Generate Student Payment Receipts) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        S -- (Access Query Dashboard as a Student)\n        (Access Query Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (Submit Medicals for Sudden Leaves) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Query Dashboard as a Student) &lt;.. (Submit Student Queries) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Submit Medicals for Sudden Leaves) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Class Teachers) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Submit Student Queries) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Class Teachers) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        \n        (Send Notifications to Students) -- SR\n\n        VP -- (Broadcast Announcements)\n        (Broadcast Announcements) ..&gt; (Send Messages as the Principal) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Send Messages as the Principal) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Users) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        VP -- (Access Event Management Dashboard)\n        (Access Event Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Create Events) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Event Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Events) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Event Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Delete Events) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Create Events) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Users): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Events) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Users): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Delete Events) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Users): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        VP -- (Access Staff Management Dashboard)\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Schedule Meetings) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Add Staff Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Remove Staff Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Staff Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Staff Members) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Schedule Meetings) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Users) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Staff Members) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Users): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        VP -- (Access Student Management Dashboard)\n        (Access Student Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (view Enrollment Information) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Student Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Generate Enrollment Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Generate Enrollment Reports) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        VP -- (Access Financial Management Dashboard)\n        (Access Financial Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Monitor Student Payments) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Financial Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (View School Budget) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Financial Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Plan School Budget) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Financial Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update School Budget) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Plan School Budget) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update School Budget) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        \n        (Access Financial Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Generate Financial Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Financial Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Withdraw Funds from School Account) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Financial Management Dashboard) &lt;.. (Deposit Funds to School Account) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Withdraw Funds from School Account) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Principal) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Deposit Funds to School Account) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Principal) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Send Notifications to Vice Principal) -- VPR\n\n        P -- (Access Administrative Dashboard)\n        (Access Administrative Dashboard) &lt;.. (View Policies) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Administrative Dashboard) &lt;.. (Create Policies) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Administrative Dashboard) &lt;.. (Update Policies) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access Administrative Dashboard) &lt;.. (Delete Policies) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Create Policies) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Vice Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Update Policies) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Vice Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n        (Delete Policies) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Vice Principal): &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Send Notifications to Principal) -- PR\n\n        A -- (Create User Accounts and Access Permissions)\n        (Create User Accounts and Access Permissions) &lt;.. (Add User) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Create User Accounts and Access Permissions) &lt;.. (Delete User) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Create User Accounts and Access Permissions) &lt;.. (Modify Permissions) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        A -- (Oversee Overall Functionality and Performance)\n        (Oversee Overall Functionality and Performance) &lt;.. (Oversee School Management) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Oversee Overall Functionality and Performance) &lt;.. (View School Staticstics) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Oversee Overall Functionality and Performance) &lt;.. (View System Staticstics) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        A -- (Ensure Security and Integrity of the Platform)\n        (Ensure Security and Integrity of the Platform) &lt;.. (Encrypt Data) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Ensure Security and Integrity of the Platform) &lt;.. (Regular Data Backups) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        A -- (Generate Reports)\n        (Generate Reports) &lt;.. (User Engagement Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Generate Reports) &lt;.. (Performance Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Generate Reports) &lt;.. (System Utilization Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Generate Reports) &lt;.. (Content Popularity Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Generate Reports) &lt;.. (Monthly Attendance Reports) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        U -- (Enter the Attendance Daily)\n        (Enter the Attendance Daily) ..&gt; (Verify Using Fingerprint) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        U -- (Login)\n        (Login) ..&gt; (Validate User) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        U -- (Access User Profile)\n        (Access User Profile) &lt;.. (View User Information) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n        (Access User Profile) &lt;.. (Update User Profile) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        U -- (Comminication)\n        (Comminication) &lt;.. (Send Messages) : &lt;&lt;extend&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Send Messages) ..&gt; (Send Notifications to Users) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n\n        (Send Notifications to Users) -- UR\n\n        U -- (Logout)\n        (Logout) ..&gt; (Confirm) : &lt;&lt;include&gt;&gt;\n}\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="TQ9qWW0fFH-PGkYJ7KQQ-1">
